<h5 id="subject_774557">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=36b752c53b0f301795115ca6597f7676&amp;topic=82161.msg774557#msg774557" rel="nofollow">Re: 钢之守护神RPG（メタリックガーディアンRPG）-上级规则书</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_774557'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_774557'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #2 于:</strong> 2016-01-25, 周一 12:38:59 &#187;</div>
